# URL the contact form posts to (e.g. a Formspree/Basin endpoint).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ because the static-export site submits directly from the browser,
# so the value is compiled into the client bundle and is public by design —
# never put secrets or private keys here.
# Copy this file to .env.local and set the real value. Never commit real endpoints.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORM_ENDPOINT=
